<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Google Extension on 記錄用</title><link>https://aben20807.github.io/tags/google-extension/</link><description>Recent content in Google Extension on 記錄用</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-tw</language><managingEditor>aben20807@gmail.com (Huang, Po-Hsuan 黃柏瑄 (aben20807))</managingEditor><webMaster>aben20807@gmail.com (Huang, Po-Hsuan 黃柏瑄 (aben20807))</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 12:10:57 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://aben20807.github.io/tags/google-extension/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>How to Check Your Installed Chrome Extensions</title><link>https://aben20807.github.io/posts/20260127-how-to-check-your-installed-chrome-extensions/</link><pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 12:09:17 +0800</pubDate><author>aben20807@gmail.com (Huang, Po-Hsuan 黃柏瑄 (aben20807))</author><guid>https://aben20807.github.io/posts/20260127-how-to-check-your-installed-chrome-extensions/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;最近新上架了一個 Chrome 擴充功能 &lt;a href="https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/google-slides-zoom/hcfdipbanljliibhmpambhpcfifbadie" title="Google Slides Zoom" aria-label="Google Slides Zoom" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-external-link-square-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Google Slides Zoom&lt;/a&gt;，被問到怎麼確認 source code 及上架版本是同一個。因為上架都是自己額外手動打包，所以中間不免有些資安疑慮。剛好找到檢查已安裝 Chrome 擴充功能檔案內容的方法。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;順便打廣告，這個擴充功能可以讓你在 Google 簡報中使用滑鼠滾輪來放大縮小投影片內容，非常實用！&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Give Me Direct Link to Image in Google Drive</title><link>https://aben20807.github.io/posts/20230416-give-me-direct-link-to-image-google-drive/</link><pubDate>Sun, 16 Apr 2023 18:01:08 +0800</pubDate><author>aben20807@gmail.com (Huang, Po-Hsuan 黃柏瑄 (aben20807))</author><guid>https://aben20807.github.io/posts/20230416-give-me-direct-link-to-image-google-drive/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;因為圖床改回 Google Drive 了，來解決一下方便性問題。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>